      <bioghist id="aspace_3b81b0f2866b9fb7061b16612d46d16f">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Yale Journal of Criticism was founded in 1986 by junior members of Yale University faculty and sponsored by the Whitney Humanities Center.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_36038a6a028708f295cf42956005d22e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of meeting agendas and minutes, correspondence, proposals, subject files, and computer files documenting the Yale Journal of Criticism.</p>  
